  "text": "Similarly, Su et al. [CITATION_1] use the same formulation as [CITATION_2] for pose estimation. However, with their rendering pipeline they are able to generate more than 2 million synthetic images with ground truth pose annotations. They use these synthetic images to train a pose estimation network, which surpasses [CITATION_3] in viewpoint estimation accuracy. Finally, they too perform two-stage detection and pose estimation with R-CNN detections. In Sec. 4, we compare our detection and pose estimation model to [CITATION_4] and show significant increases in accuracy.",
